        Comments Off on Lee was awarded the IBM fellowship


 

Mar 166
Congratulations Dr. Gerald!  


Gerald Bortis defended and passed his PhD Thesis dissertation titled “PorchLight: A Tag-based Approach to Bug Triaging”. The defense took place last Friday and the committee was formed by André van der Hoek (Chair), Crista Lopes and James Jones.
Congratulations Dr. Gerald!


